<p>First of all the result is "2009" <em>only</em>. After longer staring some people may notice slight italics applied to "2009" part of the current "result" but it does not change the fact that as this is technical docs result shall be exact one ("2009") not anything close. This applies to many other constants on that page as well, i.e. Zend_Date::DAY which, even worse is shown with boldface, italics and result in brackets. If I understand corectly, this is to point which one day is (in case US/EU users get confiused). If so, I filled another bug report how to solve this case:       ZF-7872</p>

